title: Independent candidate Amir Inayat wins PP-93 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Independent candidate Muhammad Amir Inayat Shahani has won the election for Punjab Assembly constituency PP-93, Bhakkar-V by securing 50,425 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Independent candidate Muhammad Ziaullah Khan, who bagged 45,580 votes.
Overall votersâ€™ turn-out remained 67.61%.
